{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01BJe7GdYeNw5nKtDMrZws9J","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The problem is clear: the StatefulSet uses the default `OrderedReady` pod management policy. Pod 0 won't become \"Ready\" because it's waiting for the cluster to initialize (joining pods 1 and 2 which don't exist yet since pod 0 isn't ready). This is a chicken-and-egg problem.\n\nThe fix is to switch the StatefulSet to `Parallel` pod management policy so all 3 pods start simultaneously. When all 3 are up and can reach each other, the cluster will initialize.\n\nI need to patch the StatefulSet to use `podManagementPolicy: Parallel`.\nActually, `podManagementPolicy` is immutable on a running StatefulSet, so I'll need to delete and recreate it while preserving the PVCs.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5093,"cache_read_input_tokens":31298,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":5093},"output_tokens":21,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"aa8dfa00-9fbc-42f4-a31b-33f620dd9bcd","uuid":"61a2b16e-7944-43ac-903a-aa04f9a77806","request_id":"req_011CcfdPE7wyuxgXnPocMuop"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01BJe7GdYeNw5nKtDMrZws9J","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Classic chicken-and-egg: the default `OrderedReady` policy waits for pod 0 to be Ready before creating pods 1 and 2, but pod 0 stays unready waiting to join them. Fix: delete and recreate the StatefulSet with `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` so all 3 pods start simultaneously."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5093,"cache_read_input_tokens":31298,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":5093},"output_tokens":21,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"aa8dfa00-9fbc-42f4-a31b-33f620dd9bcd","uuid":"dac821f7-3aec-4c43-97aa-88c6e60c6921","request_id":"req_011CcfdPE7wyuxgXnPocMuop"}
